            "effect": "The grikkitog sinks its barbed teeth into the target, which must succeed at a DC 34 Reflex save or be immobilized. While immobilized, the victim takes 3d8 persistent bleed damage and the grikkitog feeds upon its flesh. The creature is immobilized until the grikkitog ends the effect as a free action or the target succeeds at a DC 38 check to Escape. The grikkitog can immobilize any number of creatures with these maws.",
